DESCRIPTION:Join us as we celebrate the official ribbon cutting of Grub Sm
 oke House! Come enjoy delicious smoked favorites\, meet the team\, and be 
 part of this exciting new chapter in our community. The ribbon will be cut
  shortly after noon with plenty of good food and fun. Grub Smokehouse: Fro
 m the Global Stage to Youngsville We’re the Milova-Garrison family\, and
  we believe the best memories are made over a great meal. Our journey to Y
 oungsville has been quite the adventure—from Executive Chef David cookin
 g for world leaders and icons like Anthony Bourdain and Snoop Dogg\, to Ch
 ief Vibe Officer Kristina growing up in a traveling circus in the Soviet U
 nion. After years of traveling through Europe and California\, we’ve fin
 ally found "home" right here in the Triangle area. Tucked beside the Works
 pace Provision Co. building\, Grub Smokehouse is our way of bringing peopl
 e together through approachable\, world-class flavor. What to expect at Gr
 ub: Made from Scratch: We start every morning fresh\, slow-smoki
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/ribbon-cutt
 ing-grub-smokehouse
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Become a Notary
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260514T053000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260514T130000
UID:412365cd0a6f2c7b456ea86ea150a961@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Become a Notary Public – Right Here at the Wake Forest Chamb
 er! Ready to boost your resume and serve your community? Wake Tech is brin
 ging its full-day Notary Public class to the Wake Forest Chamber – your 
 local hub for business resources and professional development. In this int
 eractive session\, you’ll cover the essentials: ✔️ What it means to 
 be a Notary Public ✔️ General powers\, oaths\, affidavits\, and certif
 ications ✔️ A final exam and help completing your official application
  Bonus: This instructor-led class moves at the pace of the group—so you 
 may finish early! 📘 The Notary Public Guidebook for North Carolina is i
 ncluded in the cost. 🍴 Lunch break? You're steps away from great spots 
 on White Street. 🪑 Plus\, the Chamber offers a comfortable\, profession
 al setting—no fluorescent-lit classrooms here. Open to both members and 
 non-members. Space is limited\, so register early! To qualify\, you must: 
 Be 18 or older Live or work in NC Be a legal U.S. resident Speak\, read\, 
 and write English
LOCATION:Wake Forest\, NC
URL:https://chambermaster.wakeforestchamber.org/events/details/become-a-no
 tary-29048
X-SOURCE:Wake Forest Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
